overview: The user wanted to enhance the aesthetic appeal of their sleep
  questionnaire app, which they felt was functional but lacked visual
  sophistication. The assistant initiated a comprehensive review of the app's
  styling, examining global CSS, layout, main pages, and UI components. Based on
  this analysis, the assistant identified several areas for improvement,
  including the generic color palette, plain backgrounds, and basic form
  elements. The approach involved transforming the app's visual language to
  evoke a sense of calm and professionalism. Key decisions included implementing
  a new sleep-themed color palette with deep indigo/purple and teal accents,
  redesigning the QuestionnaireForm with subtle background elements and an
  improved progress indicator, enhancing the IntroSection with a more engaging
  welcome hero and feature cards, and refining the CheckboxField for a softer,
  more inviting look. The outcome is a more polished and aesthetically pleasing
  application tailored to a sleep assessment experience.
